				<div id="head-tag">	




	
				


	
				
																					

				
	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
To reunite a family kept apart, a wedding on a cross-border bridge									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>The year-old “Remain in Mexico” policy has created a new kind of family separation. Some committed couples are getting legally married at the border to try to help their asylum cases.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
						<div class="row">
				<div id="main-media" class="small-11 small-centered large-9 columns">
