							<div class="caption-bar text-wrapper  ">
					<div class="eza-caption">José and Damaris with their daughter, Angelica, are wed on the Progreso International Bridge between Texas and Mexico, Feb. 1, 2020.  The couple hopes marriage will help Damaris and Angelica join José in the U.S. and gain asylum after they fled Honduras. </div>
